Through the Nightmares, a challenge-driven platformer set within a child’s dream, is out now on PlayStation 5 & PlayStation 4!

In Through the Nightmares, players take control of Sandman, a guardian spirit who brings peaceful sleep. But dreams turn dark when Morpheus, a corrupted deity, imprisons innocent children within an endless nightmare. To rescue them, Sandman must journey into a surreal, perilous dream world.

The children are waiting. But the dream already knows you’re here… and it will stop at nothing to ensure you never leave.

About the Game:

Ride ribbons of light and blast to block busting beats in single player or multiplayer!

Created by industry veterans with a history on Guitar Hero and DJ Hero, Aaero2 combines fast-paced action with pulse-pounding music and striking visuals. The new Black Razor Edition features exclusive content from Wired’s in-house music label Black Razor Records, alongside standout tracks from Monstercat, expanding the game’s acclaimed audio-visual experience. 

Aaero2: Black Razor Edition: features tracks made popular by Arcade Paradise, the breakout hit from Wired Productions and Nosebleed Interactive, and an enigmatic selection of songs by Lania Kea, a rising start in the Black Razor Records family.

author: PlayStation
description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10013371

Out Now - Explore the cursed lands of Gévaudan in Chronicles of the Wolf!

Migami Games teams up with PQube and PixelHeart to bring Chronicles of the Wolf to life. A star-studded collaboration featuring some of gaming’s most celebrated talent. 

Immerse yourself in a dark and haunting metroidvania adventure, narrated by Robert Belgrade (Castlevania: Symphony of the Night, Tekken, Soul Blade), with a stunning soundtrack composed by Jeffrey Montoya, and guest tracks by Óscar Araujo, both acclaimed for their work on Castlevania: Lords of Shadow.

Adding even more excitement, Bloodless — the iconic crimson adversary from the Bloodstained series — makes a special guest appearance, voiced by Kira Buckland (NieR: Automata, Genshin Impact, Street Fighter V).

Hunt the legendary Beast of Gévaudan and uncover the dark secrets lurking in a vast, open world filled with danger, mystery, and brutal boss battles.

Chronicles of the Wolf launches
